Village of EzeckielvillagefC0none12778423990searchvar1.1806402*03*****01*Ezeckiel is one of three brothers who were separated at a very young age. He never saw his brothers again. The skylord ventured in the kingdom of Topaz after an extensive search for his family, ending up in a small village. In time, Ezeckiel won the respect of all the villagers who knew his greatest wish. Knowing they couldn't do anything to help find his brothers, they decided to join the topazian movement, recommending Ezeckiel as their leader to the king. In so doing, they provided Ezeckiel with the largest adoptive family ever. He was named mayor of the small village, which was renamed after him after his death.